N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4815.2 - Form for application

State Regulations

Application for a license as a bingo supplier shall be
made on form BC-106 as prescribed by the commission. The application with
supporting material as set forth in this Part, shall be filed in duplicate with
the commission. Notes
